==English==
===Etymology===
From the {{L.}} word ''[[moveō]], [[movēre]]'' meaning to move.

===Verb===
{{en-infl-reg-other-e|mov|e|}}
# ''(Intransitive):'' To go to another place.
# ''(Intransitive):'' To go and live at another place.
# ''(Transitive):'' To take something and put it to new place.

